---
title: BBQ Chicken Drumsticks & Cheesy Mash with Bacon Gravy & Waldorf-Style Salad
description: When it comes to chicken, we’re always looking for two things: golden skin and juicy, flavourful meat. Enter sticky chicken drumsticks. They’re all that and then some—the “some” being a mouth-watering BBQ glaze that takes them above and beyond. Cheesy mash, gravy and a bacon-speckled salad truly tip this meal over the edge of deliciousness.

